ActEnterprise Cape Breton Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of State (Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency) of GARY JOSEPH CORSANO of Sydney, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office for a term of three years, in the place of Curdis Karrel, whose term has expired.
